column5: suck up!
stifle Phil... yer just jealous because you didn't think of it first.
LOL
If Doug's report turns out half as good as all this foreplay, it means he had a good week.
L M A O Connie!!!  He's buildin' us up for the "BIG" one!!!
Ya.  No wonder I can't get this thing posted, with all this carp flying around.  Jeeeze.  No winker is big enough for this kitty.  Still working the gallery.  Hang on jes a bit.
Well, it's been 48 hours. I'm going to bed.
Roy wake up it's here ...
OK Doug. Where's the report. I want it on my desk within the hour MISTER!
Hmmm, maybe he didn't catch anything and he's afraid
He could at least do like he did last year and post pics of the latrine......
Well that's what I was waiting for Roy, those were the highlight of his trip last year.
and the OFC.com sign over the seat was just perfect.
Well he needed that in the pic for the inches!
Seeing as we're waiting around for the report....what are you wearing?
Chanel #5, and a little bit of tartar sauce in the corner of my mouth from leftover bacon wrapped pike.   Oh, sorry DouG, didn't mean to brag about the fish I caught......
45 minutes to go.....
Its like watching grass grow.....
Nice legs....where's Paul?
He said he'd hold his breath until DouG posted his report.  He was purple the last time I looked.
Too funny you guys....
Keep prodding him Roy!!!... I'll bet it's not the first time you ever............... never mind.
Well?
Ok, ok, ok.  Back at work now, but I have typed my diary entries and emptied the camera.  Next is resizing the photos and uploading the pictures.  I will work on it tonight.  It was good.
Good news I was thinking of you guys last week.  Hope it was everything you expected and more.  Now get focused and post  .
ditto....
D a m n it douG, some things are more important than rocket science...................
I feel a report coming on......
He has been uploading pics..I saw them in his gallery. Joe
At least we know he made it back and i guess we can Assume he caught so many fish that he is wornout and cant type???   Art
...not sure a fellow wants to hear that about his photos...

That's ok Bubba doug! Take as long as you want  Alot of these non/seldom/infrequent/one pic wonder posters don't realize how much time and effort goes into posting an "Epic" report like I know you're preparing. I for one will wait patiently whilst you work your magic, just give a holler when she's ready.
